
@startuml Context diagram
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

' Actors
actor "User" as User

' Main System
rectangle "Dungeon Battle game\n(React + Node.js + Express)" as System

' External Systems
database "MongoDB" as MongoDB

' Relationships
User --> System : Uses the application\n(register, login, battle, market, etc.)
System --> MongoDB : Stores and retrieves data\n(Users, items, dungeons, etc.)

' Notes
note right of System
  <b>Main Technologies:</b>
  • Frontend: React (Pages + Hooks + CSS Modules)
  • Backend: Node.js + Express
  • Architecture: Routes → Controllers → Services → Models
  • Authentication: JWT + bcrypt
end note

note right of User
  Main interactions:
  • User registration
  • User login
  • Profile management
  • Energy and coins tracking
end note

@enduml